text: Gianna Guaita (born 26 April 1911, date of death unknown) was an Italian gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around event at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1911 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Italian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Italy Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:People from Busto Arsizio
